	(2919,'zlmerrill@gmail.com','caitlynpszonka@gmail.com',1726,'2015-07-20 14:23:06','I can tutor you in: Grammar','Hi Zora, I&#39;m a writer myself and I&#39;d be happy to tutor you if you&#39;re interested in meeting online. If so, please let me know how often you&#39;d like to meet, and some days and times that you&#39;re available!\r\n',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'inbox',NULL),
	(2920,'vdass1970@gmail.com','ernesttroemel2+dsg@indeedemail.com',1832,'2015-07-20 14:27:10','I can tutor you in: History and Writing','Hi Shelina D., I can tutor your student in History and Writing. I am a substitute teacher in Anaheim and San Juan Capistrano, California. I have over 10 years experience teaching US History and World History at the Junior High and High School levels. Also, I have a degree in Political Science and History from UCLA. I assume that the prep. class will be reading biographies and primary historical sources from the reading list. That is basically what we used at UCLA. In addition to the reading, you need to develop a good analysis of each work and transfer this analysis to a formal composition. You are going to have to write a good thesis statement from your analysis to hold the whole composition together, and you need a lot of supporting detail for each topic sentence in each paragraph. I could tutor you online. Let me know! \r\n       Thanks, \r\n            Ernie\r\n',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'inbox',NULL),
	(2921,'zlmerrill@gmail.com','ernesttroemel2+dsg@indeedemail.com',1832,'2015-07-20 14:41:00','I can tutor you in: Speech','Hi Zora M., I can tutor you. I am tutor Ernie. I am a substitute teacher in Anaheim and San Juan Capistrano California. I have over 10 years experience in teaching at the elementary, junior high and high school levels. The best way to speak more clearly is speak in public as often as you can. Also, reading out loud to another person is a good way to develop your speak ability. Also, you need to build up a good vocabulary. I have a degree from UCLA, and I have had to speak in public many times. I am patient and understand with my students progress. I could tutor you online. Let me know! \r\nThanks, \r\n     Ernie\r\n',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'inbox',NULL),
	(2922,'zlmerrill@gmail.com','ernesttroemel2+dsg@indeedemail.com',1832,'2015-07-20 14:50:54','I can tutor you in: Grammar','Hi Zora M., I am tutor Ernie. I sent you an email message about tutoring you in speech. Also, I see that you need a grammar tutor. I could also tutor you in grammar. I have taught grammar at the elementary, junior and high school levels for over 10 years as part of a Language Arts program. To be good at grammar you need to know some of the basic parts of speech, and how to use them in a sentence. Diagraming sentences is one of the best ways to learn the parts of speech and grammar. It is hard work, but being able to pick out the parts of speech in a sentence will also help you with your speaking ability. You need to be able to pick out the subject and the predicate of a sentence to know if you have a complete sentence that other people can understand. I could tutor you online. Let me know!\r\nThanks, \r\n    Ernie\r\n',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'inbox',NULL),
